# Mistakes I Made

❌ My verbal explanation did not match my code.

❌ I initially thought there were two traversals.

❌ I confused storing the complement with storing the array element.

❌ I said HashMap stores unique values.

Correct

HashMap stores UNIQUE KEYS.

❌ I explained "check before insert" incorrectly.

Correct Reason

Checking first prevents matching an element with itself.

❌ I accidentally mixed up Time Complexity and Space Complexity while speaking.

